metadata.name: IWD Stronger Together
metadata.description:
"Stronger Together" is a creative collaboration to celebrate International Women's Day (IWD), March 2022.

Inspired by three female led NFT projects; World of Women, Boss Beauties and Women Rise, this limited edition is created by world renown artist Miss Ritika Gupta.

Utilizing the collaborative split functionality of Foundation,
90% of proceeds will be distributed automatically to the official Ukraine donation wallet:
0x165CD37b4C644C2921454429E7F9358d18A45e14

We sincerely appreciate your support, and when we are stronger together, anything is possible!
